      "description": "CH9996_Growup_1",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "这，这是给我的吗？！……太感谢了！我会加油的！",
      "text_original": "く、くれるんですか?ありがとうございます!頑張ります!",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/mV3tuemARbj4JAlBv8P5bPgzGUIoW8OS.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_Growup_2",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "我也说不清这种感觉，但总觉得自己好像变强了……",
      "text_original": "よくわからないけど、なんだか強くなったような気が",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/zdJaNSgqnz5tM1xn5OiH5QtUc5whyfn9.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_Growup_3",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "哇！感觉全身充满了力量！这样算正常吗？！",
      "text_original": "うわぁ!体中から力が湧いてくる!こういうものなんですか?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/JQ65tdD9Ib9Sg0h5z6ylvIIgRTBL4awf.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_Growup_4",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "老师！我，我感觉自己现在无所不能！",
      "text_original": "先生!あたし今ならなんでもできそうな気がします!",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/RZ8QQFxbBKsAdcmBppCobJ4GyLu9LuML.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_Lobby_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "这里和我们的世界乍看之下相似，但又完全不同……真有趣呢。",
      "text_original": "ここって私たちの世界に似ているようで全然違って面白いんですよね",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/YS9iOsIBPV1MrGn3CYgXl0G7Vud5Obd6.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_Lobby_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "诶？接下来要去散步？……我也想去！老师，拜托您带上我吧！",
      "text_original": "えっ?今から散歩?私も行きたいです!連れて行ってください!先生!",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/nqyA2yyozauzMDl351OrlknriGFp2N7N.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_Lobby_3",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "这个世界真有意思！不管什么都是！",
      "text_original": "何から何まで面白い世界ですねここ",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/oiHQSjprylUFz3m9CN0XSWRAO4zGscNJ.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_Lobby_4",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "虽然只是因为偶然才来到这里，但我真的觉得很幸运！",
      "text_original": "偶然ではありましたけどここに来てよかったです",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/eBEQwvqUw880huv2sJDr5S1vLSadjYXv.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_Lobby_5",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "老师您呢？我们来了以后……您的每一天有没有也变得有趣一些呢？",
      "text_original": "先生はどうですか?私たちが来てから毎日がちょっとは楽しくなりました?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/ZnYYOkiNOgnk88RwYqN7nufhJF2eH7W1.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_LogIn_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "啊！老师！等您好久啦！今天要做些什么？",
      "text_original": "先生、お待ちしてました。今日は何をするんですか?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/UjZ2KE5CwY4RIdIbLIUwzybtptFHuvgg.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_LogIn_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "老师，欢迎您！有什么我能帮忙做的事情吗？",
      "text_original": "おかえりなさい先生私にできること何かありますか",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/iK4yIIeeHQAGWkakNQ1eTgKwg3LJ45WH.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_MemorialLobby_1_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "唔……感觉应该没什么不同……",
      "text_original": "うーんー特に変わったところは、なさそうかな。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/A8ptHTltuOj7kx1NucmZRgpc3G0285r7.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_MemorialLobby_1_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "……老师，您的表情为什么这么紧张？ 不就是台发球机而已嘛。",
      "text_original": "先生?顔がこわばってません?ただのバッティングマシーンですって",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/GCDbsoXow8WRm9YdYh2f9fu0xnZHSqhS.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_MemorialLobby_2_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "好的！但我想应该没问题的。",
      "text_original": "はい!でも多分大丈夫です!",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/H2OOfBJ816FCEEvdPN3rx95xJ58xSZUN.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_MemorialLobby_2_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "打棒球这件事，我还是很有自信的。",
      "text_original": "バッティングにはそれなりに自信がありますから",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/0BWyUCcJjFIZoqZ0KdhNDMlrJ4du8Nnn.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_MemorialLobby_3_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "……怎么了？您干嘛一副怀疑的样子。",
      "text_original": "何ですか?その疑いの眼差しは",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/UL8WQpClyLpaUDbsa0dzWkSnTRVSMnAI.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_MemorialLobby_3_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "那我们就来打个赌吧？",
      "text_original": "じゃあ、賭けでもします?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/WHu43S0G4bDYjy3CrXYJwxMnewH0eW4b.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_MemorialLobby_4_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "如果我没有在3球以内打中，就老老实实下场。",
      "text_original": "3球以内に打てなかったら、おとなしく打席を離れます",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/jaDU6JEcjrLWaN15tvDoFlD0BSSQrO1M.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_MemorialLobby_4_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "但只要我打中了1个球，您就在那边的自动贩卖机买罐饮料请我喝！",
      "text_original": "その代わり、もし一球でも打てたら、そこの自販機で飲み物をおごってください",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/3yw0DiU8Gy2IczXPdeyv8rG0kSOPRNLz.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_MemorialLobby_5_1",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "怎么样？ 老师也觉得这样不错吧？",
      "text_original": "どうですか?先生にとっても悪い話じゃないですよね?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/oljUnEaJaoOqcWd7qnehnJqkDk6P6xwz.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_MemorialLobby_5_2",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "……嘿嘿。",
      "text_original": "へへー",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/ADFPsdJVG8O5SCLGTcsgXREtNIiGAKip.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_Relationship_Up_1",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "该怎么说才好呢……总觉得只说句谢谢似乎远远不够呢……",
      "text_original": "なんて言ったらいいんですかね?ありがとうございます!じゃあ全然足りない気がします",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/NFoxeKyYPLx2wdMusrFvRUrNE8272XpH.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_Relationship_Up_2",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "诶，诶？是给我的吗？真的要送给我吗……？",
      "text_original": "え?えぇ?あたしにですか?ほんとにいいんですか?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/LPbwhCdebtUqKtLMWbRqRkcJ5ox2XDCE.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_Relationship_Up_3",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "感觉自己一直都在受老师照顾呢，哈哈……",
      "text_original": "先生には助けられてばかりですね",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/rDApjhawBGEtPkMixCVzdiYszWwq8qAP.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_Relationship_Up_4",
      "category": "growup",
      "text": "自从来到这里，每一天都过得很开心……这一定都多亏了老师。",
      "text_original": "ここに来てから楽しいことばかりなのは、きっと先生のおかげなんだと思います。",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/DNquXzwILVS8RfnQYRmsBfVH7fXlLtjH.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_Season_Birthday_Player",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "Happy birthday！祝您生日快乐，老师！您有什么想要的东西吗？",
      "text_original": "ハッピーバースデー!お誕生日おめでとうございます先生!何か欲しいものはありますか?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/XPGRSocN8BFPZI3cSPKJ4nSXyDRqnqVc.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_Season_Halloween",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "万圣节到了……！老师！我们也换身衣服出去玩吧！",
      "text_original": "ハロウィーン!先生、あたしたちも何かかぶりに行きましょう!",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/FaqEtjXBZDIKY8d0wVaEqttzHq1wWuvh.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_Season_NewYear",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "新年快乐，老师！时间过得可真快呀……今年也请您多多关照了！老师！",
      "text_original": "あけましておめでとうございます先生！今年もよろしくお願いします先生",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/HfSVIlfno6s0e8gw2J6bD65MSYfLv5kf.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_Season_Xmas",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "这里也有圣诞节吗？！那，是不是能看到飞翔的圣诞老人？！",
      "text_original": "ここにもクリスマスがあるんですか?じゃあじゃあサンタさんが飛んでるところ見れますかね?",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/7d6NDyU9DhytWdEE3bHpBu3d0eHiMUxg.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "CH9996_Title",
      "category": "lobby",
      "text": "Blue Archive！",
      "text_original": "ブルーアーカイブ",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/j9f9lwKbxZPjaFQjLhIE2jR6hnaxtm9j.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch9996_formation_in_2",
      "category": "formation",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "できる限り頑張ります！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/original/jp/ch9996_formation_in_2.ogg"
    },
    {
      "description": "ch9996_formation_in_1",
      "category": "formation",
      "text": "",
      "text_original": "わ、私も行っていいんですか！？やったー！",
      "file": "//static.kivo.wiki/voices/students/%E4%BD%90%E5%A4%A9%20%E6%B3%AA%E5%AD%90/original/jp/ch9996_formation_in_1.ogg"
    }
  ],
